title: "The Florida Aquarium" slab serif caps
content:
Hi everyone,

Can someone ID the following font for me please?

Many thanks

Yury

[http://i45.tinypic.com/2ag41me.png](http://web.archive.org/web/20100103070840/http:/i45.tinypic.com/2ag41me.png)
author: yury90

comments.content: This typeface is very poorly drawn, which makes me suspect it’s an amateur effort, probably freeware or shareware.

I have a feeling that this was traced (not automatically) from a scan of an existing logo by somebody who isn’t a font designer.

- Lex
